origDescription:
Own a part of history! Spells Of Genesis are the first-ever collectibles on any blockchain (predating even Punks, Curio Cards, and Mooncats) and this card is the first depiction of an ape on an NFT.

Many Counterparty wallets have been lost over the years, thus circulation is likely far lower than stated.

Mint Date: 19/12/2015.
